OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774725063
OL,3,CErith fire causes huge smoke plume
OL,4,Cover South East London
OL,6,FPeople are being told to keep their
OL,7,Fwindows shut, after 400 tonnes of
OL,8,Fscrap metal was on fire in Erith.
OL,10,FSmoke plumes are traveling as far as
OL,11,FDartford.
OL,13,FLondon Fire Brigade were called to the
OL,14,Fblaze just before 5am on Saturday.
OL,16,FTwelve fire engines and around 80
OL,17,Ffirefighters were needed to bring the
OL,18,Fflames at a scrap metal recycling yard
OL,19,Fon Manor Road in Erith under control.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
