OL,3,CErith fire causes huge smoke plume
OL,4,Cover South East London
OL,6,FFirefighters are expected to remain at
OL,7,Fthe scene for the rest of the day.
OL,9,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Richard
OL,10,FArnold, who is at the scene, said:
OL,11,F"The fire is producing a significant
OL,12,Famount of smoke in the vicinity, which
OL,13,Fis moving east towards Dartford.
OL,15,F"We strongly urge people who live or
OL,16,Fwork nearby to keep windows and doors
OL,17,Fclosed and avoid the area where
OL,18,Fpossible."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
